<div class="container mt-3 mb-5">
    <h2 class="mb-4">
        🔐 Privacy Policy
    </h2>

    <p class="lead text-muted">
        Your privacy is important to us. This document outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data while using the Document Storage System.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4 class="mt-4">🔎 Data Collection</h4>
    <p>We collect only essential data required for your authentication and access control:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email address and user name (for login and roles)</li>
        <li>Uploaded document metadata (title, size, date, uploader)</li>
        <li>No sensitive personal information is stored</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🔒 Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        All documents are securely stored and access is granted based on user roles and permissions. We follow secure coding and storage practices.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🚫 Third-Party Sharing</h4>
    <p>
        We do not share your data with any third parties. Your information remains within the system.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">📅 Policy Updates</h4>
    <p>
        This policy may be updated periodically to reflect improvements or changes in functionality. Please revisit this page to stay informed.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <p class="text-muted small">
        If you have any concerns or questions, feel free to contact the administrator.
    </p>
</div>
